:115 in memcpy\nShadow bytes around the buggy address:\n  0x7548964ffd80: 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\n  0x7548964ffe00: 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\n  0x7548964ffe80: 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\n  0x7548964fff00: 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\n  0x7548964fff80: 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\n=>0x754896500000: f1 f1 f1 f1 02 f2 02 f2 04 f2[04]f2 00 00 00 00\n  0x754896500080: f2 f2 f2 f2 00 00 00 00 f2 f2 f2 f2 00 00 00 00\n  0x754896500100: 00 00 00 00 f3 f3 f3 f3 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\n  0x754896500180: 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\n  0x754896500200: 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\n  0x754896500280: 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00\nShadow byte legend (one shadow byte represents 8 application bytes):\n  Addressable:           00\n  Partially addressable: 01 02 03 04 05 06 07 \n  Heap left redzone:       fa\n  Freed heap region:       fd\n  Stack left redzone:      f1\n  Stack mid redzone:       f2\n  Stack right redzone:     f3\n  Stack after return:      f5\n  Stack use after scope:   f8\n  Global redzone:          f9\n  Global init order:       f6\n  Poisoned by user:        f7\n  Container overflow:      fc\n  Array cookie:            ac\n  Intra object redzone:    bb\n  ASan internal:           fe\n  Left alloca redzone:     ca\n  Right alloca redzone:    cb\n==1514==ABORTING\n", "timestamp": "2026-04-13T06:04:45.812190+00:00"}
